This journal is the culmination of tools and practices that I have been implementing over the years to become a magnet for my dreams and desires and I am so honored I finally get to share it with the world.

If you are looking for a quick sweat sesh this holiday season, I’ve gotchu! This is my favorite workouts, plus it’s short and efficient. Give it a go and let me know what you think!

1. Down dog Push-up 
2. Sumo squats 
3. Plank jacks
4. Curtsy lunges 
5. Hand release push-ups
6. Cross over jacks
7. Leg raises
8. Side planks crunches 
9. Squat jacks 
10. Side lunges 
11. Diamond push-ups 
12. Burpees 

just like the song, 12 Days of Christmas: 

* Do 1 down dog push up.
* Do 2 sumo squats + 1 down dog push-up.
* Do 3 plank jacks, + 2 sumo squats, + 1 down dog push-up.
* Do 4 curtsy lunges, 3 plank jacks, + 2 sumo squats, + 1 down dog push-up.
* Keep going until you get to 12 burpees.   #readysetwerk #holidayworkouts #wod #workoutholidayedition #holigays #leholiday #holidayworkout #12daysofchristmasworkout #fullbodyworkout #bodyweightworkout

ꕀ 10 v-ups
ꕀ Rest for a minute repeat 4 more times.
